subject: Marathon Running
lead_paragraph: The Olympic bronze medalist Deena Kastor won the women’s half-marathon, and Terefe Yea of Ethiopia finished first in the men’s marathon at the Arizona Rock ’n’ Roll races Sunday in Phoenix.
